				<h2>The Low Response Rate Crisis</h2>
				<p>Most businesses face this painful reality:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Email open rates below 20% (most emails never even get seen)</li>
					<li>Click-through rates under 2% (almost no one takes action)</li>
					<li>Promotions that generate little to no sales</li>
					<li>Customers ignoring your messages completely</li>
					<li>Growing sense that "email doesn't work anymore"</li>
				</ul>

